<hor. epist. 1.10.1>	  Vrbis amatorem Fuscum saluere iubemus
<hor. epist. 1.10.2>	ruris amatores, hac in re scilicet una
<hor. epist. 1.10.3>	multum dissimiles, ad cetera paene gemelli
<hor. epist. 1.10.4>	fraternis animis, quicquid negat alter, et alter,
<hor. epist. 1.10.5>	adnuimus pariter, uetuli notique columbi.               
